data.description: Beautifully maintained 6 bedroom, 4 bath in fabulous McKendree Park! Gorgeous, custom stonework and a covered rocking chair front porch. Open Floor Plan with 2-story Entry Foyer and large separate dining room. Your own office features custom built-ins. Master bedroom on Main and beautifully remodeled Bath with oversized tiled shower. Spacious Kitchen features soft close hinges on cabinets, Island, Pantry open to Breakfast Area and Family Room. Luxurious Master Suite with Sitting Area, ensuite bath features His & Hers vanities, oversized tile shower and jetted tub. Full, Finished Basement.
